/use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kch1665703202145.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kch1665703202145.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kch1665703202145.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kch1665703202145\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Parses a specified XML stream.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"kch1665703202145__topic_d136280e1_d136281e1_d136282e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104kch1665703202145_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"kch1665703202145__codeblock_qpw_wng_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">PARSE(XmlDocument, Validation)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kch1665703202145__section_twx_xng_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1216947e56\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16268e1_d16269e1_d16270e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">PARSE parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16268e1_d16269e1_d16270e1__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16268e1_d16269e1_d16270e1__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16268e1_d16269e1_d16270e1__entry__3\">Direction</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16268e1_d16269e1_d16270e1__entry__4\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16268e1_d16269e1_d16270e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">XmlDocument</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16268e1_d16269e1_d16270e1__entry__2\">String </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16268e1_d16269e1_d16270e1__entry__3\">IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16268e1_d16269e1_d16270e1__entry__4\"> XML document to be parsed; maximum size is\n                        10240000 bytes (nearly 10 MB). <p class=\"p\">The encoding of the XML document is always\n                           UTF-8; do not specify a different encoding in the XML header.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16268e1_d16269e1_d16270e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Validation</var></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16268e1_d16269e1_d16270e1__entry__2\">Boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16268e1_d16269e1_d16270e1__entry__3\">IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16268e1_d16269e1_d16270e1__entry__4\">Determines whether the XML parser will validate\n                        the XML it reads. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kch1665703202145__section_zhm_24g_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1216947e137\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kch1665703202145__p_d136328e1_d136329e1_d136330e1\">If a fatal error occurs during parsing,\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">-151</code> is returned, unless the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">FATALERROR</span> operation\n            returns a different negative value. In this case that value is returned instead.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">PARSE return values</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__1\">Number</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__2\">Error</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__3\">Success</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__1\">–57</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__2\">&lt;UACTERR_NO_INSTANCE&gt;</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__3\">No handler instance set.<p class=\"p\">If you invoke the\n                              <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSE</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSEFILE</span> operation\n                           without having set a handler instance, they will return this error and\n                           will not parse anything.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__1\">–151</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__2\">&lt;UACTERR_EXCEPTION_THROWN&gt;</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kch1665703202145__table_d16277e1_d16278e1_d16279e1__entry__3\">A fatal error has occured but there is no\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">FATALERROR</span> operation implemented.<p class=\"p\">A\n                              <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">FATALERROR</span> operation is available but it returns\n                           nothing or a value &gt;= 0.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">A fatal error is deemed unrecoverable, by the SAX parser.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kch1665703202145__section_nbk_34g_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1216947e241\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kch1665703202145__p_d136298e1_d136299e1_d136300e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSE</span> operation invokes the\n            SAX parser built into Uniface and the SAX operations of the handler instance. If any\n            handler operation returns a negative value, parsing stops and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSE</span>\n            returns with that negative value.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kch1665703202145__p_d136301e1_d136302e1_d136303e1\">For larger documents, you must use the\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSEFILE</span> operation.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104kch1665703202145_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"kch1665703202145__codeblock_zn4_n4g_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">activate $50.setHandler($instancename)\nTF2=\"&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\"?&gt;%%^%/\n&lt;note&gt;%%^%/\n &lt;to&gt;Tove&lt;/to&gt;%%^%/\n &lt;from&gt;Jani&lt;/from&gt;%%^%/\n &lt;heading&gt;Reminder&lt;/heading&gt;%%^%/\n&lt;/note&gt;%%^\"\nactivate $50.parse(\"TF2\", \"T\")</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ttv1665703202809.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>PARSEFILE</a><p>Parses an XML document in the specified file.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529151\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529151\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "PARSE Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Parses a specified XML stream. Explain this code PARSE(XmlDocument, Validation) Copy Parameters Table 1. PARSE parameters Parameter Data Type Direction Description XmlDocument String IN XML document to be parsed; maximum size is 10240000 bytes (nearly 10 MB). The encoding of the XML document is always UTF-8; do not specify a different encoding in the XML header. Validation Boolean IN Determines whether the XML parser will validate the XML it reads. Return Values If a fatal error occurs during parsing, -151 is returned, unless the FATALERROR operation returns a different negative value. In this case that value is returned instead. Table 2. PARSE return values Number Error Description 0 Success –57 <UACTERR_NO_INSTANCE> No handler instance set. If you invoke the PARSE or PARSEFILE operation without having set a handler instance, they will return this error and will not parse anything. –151 <UACTERR_EXCEPTION_THROWN> A fatal error has occured but there is no FATALERROR operation implemented. A FATALERROR operation is available but it returns nothing or a value >= 0. A fatal error is deemed unrecoverable, by the SAX parser. Description The PARSE operation invokes the SAX parser built into Uniface and the SAX operations of the handler instance. If any handler operation returns a negative value, parsing stops and PARSE returns with that negative value. For larger documents, you must use the PARSEFILE operation. Explain this code activate $50.setHandler($instancename) TF2=\"<?xml version=\"1.0\"?>%%^%/ <note>%%^%/ <to>Tove</to>%%^%/ <from>Jani</from>%%^%/ <heading>Reminder</heading>%%^%/ </note>%%^\" activate $50.parse(\"TF2\", \"T\") Copy Related Links PARSEFILE Parses an XML document in the specified file. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}